  date text,
  time text,
  has_seating_outdoors text CHECK (has_seating_outdoors IN (True, False)),
  has_vegetarian_options text CHECK (has_vegetarian_options IN (True, False)),
  phone_number text,
  rating text,
  address text,
  number_of_seats int CHECK (number_of_seats IN (1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6)),
  price_range text CHECK (price_range IN (cheap, moderate, pricey, ultra high-end)),
  location text,
  category text,
